295
00:17:35,600 --> 00:17:36,800
I hope you don't mind waiting here alone.

296
00:17:36,800 --> 00:17:38,460
I'll go find something to eat.

297
00:18:01,280 --> 00:18:02,880
What are you thinking about?

298
00:18:04,560 --> 00:18:07,360
