Didn't you finish work at 12?

315
00:19:23,720 --> 00:19:25,040
Where did you go?

316
00:19:25,680 --> 00:19:27,520
Did you go with...?

317
00:19:28,160 --> 00:19:29,720
Yesterday, I…

318
00:19:32,920 --> 00:19:33,840
Hello?

319
00:19:34,840 --> 00:19:36,200
Okay, I'm coming down.

320
00:19:36,800 --> 00:19:38,200
I'll go get the delivery.

321
00:19:49,440 --> 00:19:50,040
Hello.

322
00:19:50,160 --> 00:19:51,600
Your food delivery.

323
00:19:51,760 --> 00:19:52,360
Thank you.

324
00:19:56,680 --> 00:19:57,880
How did you get hurt?

325
00:19:58,080 --> 00:19:58,920
I accidentally fell

326
00:19:58,920 --> 00:20:00,240
on the road.

327
00:20:01,200 --> 00:20:02,730
You should go to a hospital.

328
00:20:02,760 --> 00:20:03,800
You are my last order.

329
00:20:03,800 --> 00:20:04,800
I'll go now.

330
00:20:06,520 --> 00:20:07,120
By the way,

331
00:20:07,160 --> 00:20:08,890
