354
00:20:52,880 --> 00:20:53,680
Okay, thanks.

355
00:20:53,760 --> 00:20:54,400
It's okay.

356
00:21:34,600 --> 00:21:35,520
Are you okay?

357
00:21:36,360 --> 00:21:37,160
Yes, I'm fine.

358
00:21:37,360 --> 00:21:39,220
Should I take you to the hospital?

359
00:21:41,120 --> 00:21:43,120
Uncle Lin, take him to the hospital.

360
00:21:43,160 --> 00:21:45,020
No, no, no, it's not appropriate.

361
00:21:45,040 --> 00:21:46,040
