465
00:26:26,200 --> 00:26:27,440
and won't be able to get married.

466
00:26:27,440 --> 00:26:28,520
However, she's also afraid that

467
00:26:28,520 --> 00:26:29,920
you'll get cheated

468
00:26:30,160 --> 00:26:30,880
by those

469
00:26:31,000 --> 00:26:32,600
