541
00:30:00,720 --> 00:30:01,280
You should go too.

542
00:30:01,280 --> 00:30:02,320
Get to know them.

543
00:30:04,000 --> 00:30:05,520
I don't think I'll go.

544
00:30:06,000 --> 00:30:07,120
Go and get to know each other.

545
00:30:07,120 --> 00:30:08,450
You guys can be friends.

546
00:30:08,600 --> 00:30:08,920
That's right.

547
00:30:08,920 --> 00:30:09,920
What do you think?

548
00:30:09,960 --> 00:30:11,120
After getting his master's degree,

549
00:30:11,120 --> 00:30:12,320
he joined his family's business.

550
00:30:12,320 --> 00:30:13,320
He's a practical person.

551
00:30:13,320 --> 00:30:15,180
He worked his way up as a sales rep.

552
00:30:15,280 --> 00:30:15,960
He's not

553
00:30:16,120 --> 00:30:17,520
