558
00:30:24,800 --> 00:30:27,130
It's a company that produces briefcases.

559
00:30:27,760 --> 00:30:28,560
That's right.

560
00:30:28,720 --> 00:30:29,480
And...

561
00:30:30,360 --> 00:30:31,760
he's also

562
00:30:31,920 --> 00:30:32,720
going to that investment meeting.

563
00:30:32,720 --> 00:30:33,650
If you have time,

564
00:30:33,800 --> 00:30:34,880
you could come with me.

565
00:30:34,880 --> 00:30:36,520
I'll introduce you to each other.

566
00:30:36,520 --> 00:30:37,180
Take a look.

567
00:30:37,880 --> 00:30:38,840
I'll take a look at it later.

568
00:30:38,840 --> 00:30:40,370
I'll go see Yuanyuan first.

569
00:30:43,480 --> 00:30:45,400
Zhenjiang has changed so much.

570
00:30:51,520 --> 00:30:52,480
Don't go.

571
00:30:52,640 --> 00:30:54,440
That man is not handsome enough.

572
00:30:56,400 --> 00:30:57,880
Little girl.

573
00:31:18,120 --> 00:31:19,720
What are you thinking about?

574
00:31:22,640 --> 00:31:25,360
I'm thinking is it too noisy here

